'There is no time to talk. Easterlings are cresting the hill and about to crash into the walls of this town.\n\n'Are you ready to join the defence?'
'I do not know how they got up from the river so quickly, but I am glad you were here to aid us.'
'Are you ready to make a stand with us and defend Harwick?'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This is an instanced public questing area.</rgb>
Easterlings have come across the river and are marching on Harwick.
